{"article_id":"pIx0uydseiZtJnW7","edus":[{"id":0,"text":"A lawsuit","depth":5},{"id":1,"text":"filed by MGM Resorts International , owner of the Las Vegas hotel","depth":6},{"id":2,"text":"from which Stephen Paddock fatally shot 58 people and wounded hundreds ,","depth":6},{"id":3,"text":"is drawing outrage from survivors of the deadliest mass shooting in U.S. history .","depth":4},{"id":4,"text":"The suit","depth":7},{"id":5,"text":"filed against hundreds of the victims of the rampage Oct. 1 outside the Mandalay Bay hotel","depth":7},{"id":6,"text":"claims","depth":6},{"id":7,"text":"the entertainment giant has `` no liability of any kind . ''","depth":5},{"id":8,"text":"MGM said in a statement","depth":6},{"id":9,"text":"the filing was meant to provide a `` timely resolution '' for shooting victims","depth":7},{"id":10,"text":"who sued or will sue in the aftermath of the attack during the Route 91 Harvest Festival .","depth":7},{"id":11,"text":"MGM said","depth":6},{"id":12,"text":"litigation","depth":8},{"id":13,"text":"filed against it","depth":8},{"id":14,"text":"`` must be dismissed . ''","depth":7},{"id":15,"text":"\" The unforeseeable events of October 1st affected thousands of people in Las Vegas and throughout North America , ''","depth":4},{"id":16,"text":"MGM Resorts spokeswoman Debra DeShong said in a statement .","depth":4},{"id":17,"text":"`` From the day of this tragedy , we have focused on the recovery of those","depth":4},{"id":18,"text":"impacted by the despicable act of one evil individual . ''","depth":4},{"id":19,"text":"More :","depth":4},{"id":20,"text":"'There ' s people shot everywhere ! ' :","depth":5},{"id":21,"text":"Las Vegas shooting 911 calls released","depth":5},{"id":22,"text":"More :","depth":4},{"id":23,"text":"Documents detail terror , chaos during deadly Las Vegas shooting rampage","depth":4},{"id":24,"text":"Brian Claypool , a survivor of the rampage","depth":8},{"id":25,"text":"who represents 75 survivors and victims ' family members ,","depth":8},{"id":26,"text":"called MGM 's lawsuit `` a stunt ''","depth":8},{"id":27,"text":"that wo n't survive a court challenge .","depth":8},{"id":28,"text":"`` I am still in therapy once a week ,","depth":7},{"id":29,"text":"and this is their way","depth":10},{"id":30,"text":"of trying to solve the problem , ''","depth":10},{"id":31,"text":"he said .","depth":9},{"id":32,"text":"`` It ' s shifting responsibility","depth":9},{"id":33,"text":"and minimizing their blatant negligence . ''","depth":9},{"id":34,"text":"Robert Eglet ,","depth":10},{"id":35,"text":"whose firm represents hundreds of people in the case ,","depth":10},{"id":36,"text":"dismissed MGM 's claim as `` outrageous ''","depth":9},{"id":37,"text":"and accused the company of trying to intimidate victims .","depth":8},{"id":38,"text":"Very few of his clients have filed suit","depth":9},{"id":39,"text":"and some never will ,","depth":9},{"id":40,"text":"he said .","depth":8},{"id":41,"text":"`` In my 30 years of practice , this is the most reprehensible behavior","depth":9},{"id":42,"text":"I have ever seen a defendant engage in , ''","depth":9},{"id":43,"text":"Eglet said .","depth":8},{"id":44,"text":"`` They are trying to victimize these people twice . ''","depth":7},{"id":45,"text":"MGM 's lawsuit claims","depth":9},{"id":46,"text":"the case must be dealt with in federal court under terms of the post-9/11 Safety Act ,","depth":10},{"id":47,"text":"which provides incentives for development and deployment of anti-terrorism technologies .","depth":10},{"id":48,"text":"The company says","depth":11},{"id":49,"text":"the security firm","depth":14},{"id":50,"text":"it contracted for the concert ,","depth":14},{"id":51,"text":"CSC , was approved by the Department of Homeland Security ,","depth":13},{"id":52,"text":"thus released from liability under the act .","depth":12},{"id":53,"text":"Eglet and Claypool said","depth":11},{"id":54,"text":"that release does not extend to the hotel .","depth":11},{"id":55,"text":"`` The Safety Act does n't apply to them ,","depth":12},{"id":56,"text":"it applies to CSC , ''","depth":12},{"id":57,"text":"Eglet said .","depth":11},{"id":58,"text":"`` MGM has nothing","depth":11},{"id":59,"text":"to do with CSC . ''","depth":11},{"id":60,"text":"Eglet said","depth":10},{"id":61,"text":"there was no reason","depth":11},{"id":62,"text":"to file the suit","depth":11},{"id":63,"text":"since the issue of jurisdiction is already being argued in court .","depth":9},{"id":64,"text":"He said","depth":9},{"id":65,"text":"MGM is `` judge shopping . ''","depth":10},{"id":66,"text":"`` They are trying to find a judge","depth":13},{"id":67,"text":"they like , ''","depth":13},{"id":68,"text":"he said .","depth":12},{"id":69,"text":"`` All","depth":13},{"id":70,"text":"they have done","depth":13},{"id":71,"text":"is cause a tremendous amount of stress ,","depth":13},{"id":72,"text":"pouring gasoline on the fire . ''","depth":13},{"id":73,"text":"Carl Tobias , a professor at the University of Richmond School of Law in Virginia , said","depth":10},{"id":74,"text":"the company may be able to convince a federal judge with its arguments ,","depth":11},{"id":75,"text":"but that would come at a price .","depth":11},{"id":76,"text":"`` Even if MGM is successful ,","depth":11},{"id":77,"text":"that may not outweigh the adverse publicity for the company","depth":12},{"id":78,"text":"that the suit generates , ''","depth":12},{"id":79,"text":"he told .","depth":10},{"id":80,"text":"`` This is just OUTRAGEOUS & WRONG , ''","depth":10},{"id":81,"text":"tweeted JoAnn Smith ,","depth":11},{"id":82,"text":"whose profile says","depth":12},{"id":83,"text":"she is a security officer in Las Vegas .","depth":12},{"id":84,"text":"Crypto Contrarian tweeted","depth":11},{"id":85,"text":"that","depth":12},{"id":86,"text":"`` being a Las Vegan ,","depth":13},{"id":87,"text":"I must speak out about this .","depth":13},{"id":88,"text":"Can MGM not see how harmful this will be ? ''","depth":10},{"id":89,"text":"Paddock fired more than 1,000 rounds from a 32nd-floor hotel room","depth":9},{"id":90,"text":"overlooking the concert .","depth":9},{"id":91,"text":"He was found dead of a self-inflicted gunshot wound in the room .","depth":8},{"id":92,"text":"Numerous lawyers in Las Vegas feature the shooting on their websites ,","depth":6},{"id":93,"text":"some calling out MGM and the concert promoter for providing inadequate security .","depth":7},{"id":94,"text":"`` A gunman","depth":12},{"id":95,"text":"bringing more than two dozen firearms into a hotel room ,","depth":13},{"id":96,"text":"including military-style assault weapons ,","depth":13},{"id":97,"text":"is almost unthinkable , ''","depth":11},{"id":98,"text":"the Ladah Law Firm says on its website .","depth":10},{"id":99,"text":"`` There are serious questions about the security procedures at the Mandalay Bay . ''","depth":9},{"id":100,"text":"The write-up says ,","depth":10},{"id":101,"text":"`` If you so much as take a casino chip off of a table","depth":11},{"id":102,"text":"you will no doubt be immediately surrounded by security guards ;","depth":11},{"id":103,"text":"yet , nothing was done in this case . ''","depth":9},{"id":104,"text":"Claypool said","depth":5},{"id":105,"text":"MGM should spend money on safety consultants , not lawyers","depth":6},{"id":106,"text":"developing `` desperate arguments ''","depth":7},{"id":107,"text":"designed to avoid responsibility .","depth":7},{"id":108,"text":"`` Fixing security would be the socially responsible thing","depth":7},{"id":109,"text":"to do , ''","depth":7},{"id":110,"text":"he said .","depth":6},{"id":111,"text":"`` But instead they ' re offending every person on the planet with their moral indignity . ''","depth":5}],"relations":[{"parent":223,"left":130,"right":222,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":130,"left":126,"right":129,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":126,"left":115,"right